{"word":"Elizaphan","slug":"elizaphan","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Elizaphan</b> <a href=\"#/H469\">H469</a> <br/> 1. A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=22'>Exo 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=4'>Lev 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=30'>Num 3:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=8'>1Ch 15:8</a><br/> 2. A prince of Zebulun<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=25'>Num 34:25</a><br/> 3. Probably identical with a Levite above<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=13'>2Ch 29:13</a>"}]}